title: Scantechnic device managment tool
description: System utilizing a modified LSTM model for detecting complex anomalies on data from physical devices in IOT. The model captures temperature anomalies in IoT device data and regulates these anomalies with a fan. The system implements a modified algorithm and real-time monitoring and control interfaces for IoT devices that contribute to data protection in IoT.

title: iEat - Food ordering and delivery application
description: iEat application provides login features, loading products to menu, adding products to cart. Also it can setup profile info such as address, phone number, credit cards. After these steps it lets user to order food via application to the desired place

title: WearPlan - System for integration with clothes shops and customers
